sgfont" id="postmessage_573731126"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573731126"&gt;二手市場再錄蝕讓成交，屯門NOVO LAND第2B期一房單位，獲區內租客轉租為買，以403萬元承接。一手業主則持貨約兩年帳面損失約52.2萬元或約11.5%。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：二手市場錄蝕不斷NOVO LAND業主持貨兩年輸逾一成 | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250824%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250824212528238-0824_00842_001.html%3Fkeywordid%3D4028828d7471d2a50174ba053e176f16%26keywordname%3D%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=4baabda5145ad185e67a8a1bcacf1856&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/fina ... &amp;amp;amp;keywordname=地產&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32016134&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=151477235468ac5d5e896267_37762557"/><published>2025-08-25T17:30:39+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5a2c4384f6cc24f160bc5d5387a1921f</id><title>🆘馬鞍山星漣海海景三房私樓劈價售出 一手業主8年狂輸超過四成</title><updated>2025-08-25T17:31:28+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-25T17:31:28+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573731138"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573731138"&gt;樓價從高位累積相當跌幅，再有近年入市的業主勁蝕沽貨，馬鞍山星漣海海景三房戶減價後以860萬港元售出，一手業主持貨約8年帳面勁蝕超過四成。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：海景三房私樓劈價售出一手業主8年狂輸超過四成 | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250825%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250825134406340-0825_00842_001.html%3Fkeywordid%3D4028828d7471d2a50174ba053e176f16%26keywordname%3D%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=9e8df1daa62bacdff73d27bbf812acf